        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "justify",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Consistently, all coda /s/ are susceptible to reduction, though it is consistently preconsonantal /s/ that favors reduction over prevocalic tokens. Additionally, in some studies, etymological /s/ appears more likely to be reduced than when the sibilant marks 2nd-person verb forms or pluralizes nouns (e.g., ¿"
        },
        {
          "text": "tiene",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": "s",
          "italic": true,
          "underline": true,
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "text": " perro",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": "s",
          "italic": true,
          "underline": true,
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "text": "?). But overall, s-reduction appears to be more conditioned by stylistic and social factors rather than strictly linguistic structures, which has lead some scholars to frame this variable as an enregistered artistic marker of reggaetón production. That is, it is a central component for distinguishing and situating the reggaetón voice amidst broader popular music soundscapes. Consider the following examples from Ivy Queen: Both were released in 2023, though \"Quién Dijo\" is written with heavy bachata and (to use the industry term) \"Tropical\" stylistics, whereas \"Bye Bye\" is encoded as a pop-infused reggaetón track. Alongside phonation differences in terms of tempo, pitch, and syllabic duration, the rate at which /s/ is retained or reduced also drastically changes. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "justify",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "justify",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "includes": [
        "media",
        "annotations",
        "label"
      ],
      "event1": {
        "uuid": "22d7e266-b85e-4420-a294-0f04e5dcf369",
        "start": 38,
        "end": 83,
        "file": "de311517-40fe-489e-bb8a-9ad01b839207",
        "type": "Video"
      },
      "event2": {
        "uuid": "cb8196ae-b0c9-449c-9066-a31cbfd78c1b",
        "start": 137,
        "end": 191,
        "file": "b9158ed2-282e-4e81-a0a2-f8c6e8da861c",
